707765f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 5th St.
707765f-a.text:
80-86 Second Avenue, east side, north to the corner of 5th Street.
June 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

707766f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 5th St.
707766f-a.text:
Second Avenue, east side, north from and including 5th Street. The
building on the N.W. corner is an old apartment house called
''The Avenue.''
June 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
